trans-unit.source: Click on the Guide link to create your Azure tokens.

trans-unit.source: Insert the "Directory (tenant) ID" and the "Client Secret". Make sure to copy the value, not the id. After that click on "Open Job Queue" in order to create the job queue.

trans-unit.source: If you are using local remember to create a job queue in every destination company as well.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruger lokalt, skal du også huske at oprette en jobkø i alle destinationsselskaber.
